佢又唔上進...唉，係香港揾個正常男仔都咁難</blockquote><br />\n理你真心定假膠<br />\n你咁on9嘅話我一定飛你"},{"pid":"edb81560cbcbd4ae92313e5ba86d27a9c7c10f49","tid":264474,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"樓主精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ecfbcd19465238314cdca1e95b2884b6cfcb9d","tid":264474,"uid":38609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"正常男仔<br />\n5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63621cc20a7088236274b77ce4d8403dd9096e4","tid":264474,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"莉莉絲之所以變成怪物<br />\n就係唔肯同呀當做愛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：聽雲海講"},{"pid":"6e8ecc86207b562bf1dc62bd9a339373a0c37847","tid":264474,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常男仔<br />\n5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我遲d變左非處無人可憐我"},{"pid":"6ae680f70d06ff44dabb34a7312fe8db12f8c300","tid":264474,"uid":47827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正常男仔<br />\n5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我遲d變左非處無人可憐我</blockquote><br />\n你確定你條仔5年黎無SP 無叫雞?"},{"pid":"ab4dc3cc3ce22aa7ae8f928b47a3e38583d0d358","tid":264474,"uid":87472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾 假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d794924a1bf10028a63319b352c8e47321d5676","tid":264474,"uid":24866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:17:26.000Z","msg":"你都係搵番個基督徒啦 你搵d世俗既話 會比佢害到你<br />\n如果你有番教會 應該都搵到既"},{"pid":"d45782c258678b9c8a092fb309b2740fd688cb51","tid":264474,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T0